```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "nekrs",
      "PrgEnv-gnu",
      "craype-accel-amd-gfx90a",
      "cray-mpich",
      "rocm",
      "sbcast"
    ],
    "libraries": [
      "mpi_gtl_hsa",
      "libnekrs.so",
      "libocca.so",
      "libnekrs-hypre-device.so",
      "libnekrs-hypre.so"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "compute_nodes": "specified by user",
      "gpus": "8 per node",
      "cores": "7 per NUMA node",
      "memory": "unlimited",
      "queue": "batch (user-configurable)",
      "time": "specified by user",
      "project_id": "specified by user",
      "other": [
        "NVME_HOME=/mnt/bb/$USER/",
        "MPICH_GPU_SUPPORT_ENABLED=1",
        "MPICH_MPIIO_HINTS=*:cray_cb_write_lock_mode=2:cray_cb_nodes_multiplier=4:striping_unit=16777216:striping_factor=specified by script:romio_cb_write=enable:romio_ds_write=disable:romio_no_indep_rw=true",
        "NEKRS_GPU_MPI=1",
        "MPICH_MPIIO_STATS=1",
        "MPICH_OFI_NIC_POLICY=NUMA",
        "NEKRS_CACHE_BCAST=1 (user-configurable)",
        "NEKRS_LOCAL_TMP_DIR=$NVME_HOME"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
